	prompt "Server profile"
	default MUC_OPCUA_PROFILE_CUSTOM
	help
	  Starting facet set for the OPC UA Server.  Each named tier seeds
	  its default facets; individual facets below remain togglable without
	  changing the selected profile.  "custom" starts from nothing.

